parameters:
"Who would have thought there'd be a path to an abandoned
lab right in the middle of town."

"So they've been continuing experiments underground with the
important machinery, even though it's not operational on the
surface."
"Maroges and Tina are likely further inside. Are you ready?"
"Yeah, of course. Let's go, Selphie-san... Rise?"

"No way, did she charge in alone because she was too
angry...?"
"What kind of image does Suelle have of Rise, I wonder..."

"Actually, when I was looking at the layout of this place, I
noticed something suspicious. So I had Rise take a different
route to check it out."
"I tried to tell Suelle as well..."

"But no matter how many times I called out, you didn't
notice because you were so focused on checking your
equipment. I thought it would be bad to disturb you."

"Oh, that's what happened... Now that you mention it, I feel
like I was checking over my gear non-stop on the way here
because I was anxious."

"Besides, Tina's specialty in combat is to repel attacks
with her power-charged blade."

"Both Rise and I specialize in long-range combat tactics, so
it's actually easier for us to fight Tina one-on-one."
"Or are you worried about me being alone?"

(Selphie's combat abilities are on par with Tina's, and her
analytical skills are even superior.)

(If Selphie says it's better for her to go alone, she must
have a plan.)
(Then all I can do is trust her and provide support.)

"Understood. Let me know if there's anything I can help
with."

"Yes, of course. Let's discuss the strategy as we move
forward."
